@startuml
title Use Case C - Personalized Recommend Flow
skinparam shadowing false

start
:BusinessSystem\ncall POST recommend;
:SearchRecAPI\nuser_profile, top_k;
:FeatureStoreAdapter\nget_user_features(user_profile)\n(preferred_tags, recent_queries,\naffinity_boost, …);
:Build **query** string:\njoin **recent_queries**;\nelse join **preferred_tags**;\nelse **"*"** (sentinel);
:SearchRecService.search(\nquery, top_k,\npreferred_tags from user features)\n**same pipeline as Use Case B**;
:Multiply each item **score**\nby **affinity_boost**;
:Re-sort by score descending;
:Expose **affinity_boost**\nin item.features;
:Return recommendation list;
stop
@enduml
